Cloak and DaggerEarth11/13/3038Enemy activity has been increasingrapidly in the earth's orbit over thepast 2 weeks.This is an important strategiclocation and we must gain controlover this area.We have moved 4 Motherships and 7fighter craft into the area.Intelligence reports we are upagainst 6 enemy supply vessels and15 fighter craft.Although our flight team areoutnumbered, we have the element ofsurprise on our side as well as newlyupgraded fighter craft.Additional: Cloaking devices are beingused by both sides.- MOTHERSHIP -Callum Blaze- AERIAL SUPPORT -Luke Forester,Jane Holly-DeanHazel PhoenixDave ValiantStefan LancasterCrusherLeslie Jacobs#